Question: A boat with white sails in the up position is sailing in the water in the image on the left.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: http://www.tallship-fan.de/images/rr2015_0757.jpg

Right image URL: http://www.tallship-fan.de/images/rr2015_0237.jpg

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the boat sailing in the water?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the sails in the up position?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the boat white?')
ANSWER3=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER3)
```
